{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/extras/kick_banner.png?t=1734574605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Little Monster is a fast-paced beat \u2018em up game where you play as Stormy, a little monster who's trying to ward off nightmare spirits while we sleep. This 2-D style beat \u2018em up combines roguelike elements with arena style gameplay. Punch, race, fly, and shoot your way through three different realms as you try and rescue your friends. Become a nightmare hunter, save your friends, and prevent the human realm from becoming a nightmare!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/extras/gif1.gif?t=1734574605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/extras/dis_banner.png?t=1734574605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Stormy, a hard hitting, fist wielding little monster who wants to follow in the footsteps of his ancestors and prevent nightmares from contaminating our dreams. Monsters train and live in the monster realm where they have access to portals that lead into our world. To remain hidden these portals appear under our beds at night and it\u2019s a monster\u2019s duty to help us, not scare us. Your job as a monster hunter is to stop these nightmares from tainting our dreams.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/extras/gif2.gif?t=1734574605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Getting fed up with the monster\u2019s interference, the nightmare spirits invade the monster realm, targeting and capturing the realm\u2019s best nightmare hunters. Caught in the middle of this during training, Stormy rushes to save his friends and stop the nightmares from corrupting the realms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/extras/features_banner.png?t=1734574605\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attack and dodge before the enemy gets a hit in. Chain combo and special attacks for a more effective take down.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monster friends can join in the fight once rescued from the deepest depths of the nightmare realm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trapped monsters appear throughout each stage! Rescue them before they disappear!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect lost pages, journey to the past, and play through 12 unlockable stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase special attack items that can assist the player if in a tough spot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race, fly, and shoot your way through 3 different special stages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The direct approach doesn\u2019t always work! Turn the tide and use a boss spirits own attack against them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose a stage perk, unlock achievements, and gain access to new items by leveling up.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734574605","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734574605","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734574605","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2503620/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734574605","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],